stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Created: Payment intent created

    Created --> Pending: Customer submits payment
    Created --> Expired: ⏰ Session timeout\n(15-30 min)
    Created --> Cancelled: Customer abandons

    Pending --> RequiresAction: 3DS / redirect needed
    Pending --> Authorized: Direct authorization\nsucceeded ✅
    Pending --> Failed: Authorization\ndeclined ❌

    RequiresAction --> Authorized: Customer completes\nauthentication ✅
    RequiresAction --> Failed: Authentication\nfailed ❌
    RequiresAction --> Expired: ⏰ Challenge timeout

    Authorized --> Captured: Merchant captures\n(immediate or delayed)
    Authorized --> PartiallyCaptured: Merchant captures\nless than auth amount
    Authorized --> Voided: Merchant voids\nbefore capture
    Authorized --> Expired: ⏰ Auth expires\n(7-30 days)

    PartiallyCaptured --> Settled: Settlement\ncompletes
    PartiallyCaptured --> PartiallyRefunded: Partial refund\ninitiated

    Captured --> Settled: Batch settlement\nT+1 to T+3

    Settled --> Refunded: Full refund\nprocessed 💰
    Settled --> PartiallyRefunded: Partial refund\nprocessed
    Settled --> Disputed: Customer files\nchargeback ⚠️

    PartiallyRefunded --> Refunded: Remaining amount\nrefunded
    PartiallyRefunded --> Disputed: Customer disputes\nremaining

    Disputed --> DisputeWon: Merchant wins\ndispute ✅
    Disputed --> DisputeLost: Merchant loses\ndispute ❌
    Disputed --> Refunded: Merchant accepts\n& refunds

    DisputeWon --> Settled: Funds returned\nto merchant
    DisputeLost --> Refunded: Funds returned\nto customer

    Failed --> [*]: Terminal state
    Expired --> [*]: Terminal state
    Cancelled --> [*]: Terminal state
    Voided --> [*]: Terminal state
    Refunded --> [*]: Terminal state

    note right of Created
        Initial state when payment
        intent is created via API
    end note

    note right of Authorized
        Funds reserved on card
        Not yet transferred
        Can be voided at no cost
    end note

    note right of Captured
        Funds will be transferred
        in next settlement batch
    end note

    note right of Settled
        Funds transferred to
        merchant account
        Refund window opens
    end note

    note right of Disputed
        Funds provisionally reversed
        Merchant must respond
        within 7-21 days
    end note

    note right of Voided
        Auth cancelled before capture
        No funds moved
        No fees charged
    end note
